    the  bill  seeks  to  repeal  the  antihijacking act of 1982 to give effect to the hague convention for the suppression of  unlawful  seizure  of  aircraft  1970  and  the  beijing  convention  of  2010  to which the government of india is a signatory  i have an objection in the case of punishment  clause  particularly  to  death  penalty  as  we  have  seen  that  race  and place  determine  who  lives  and  who  dies    i  urge  upon  the  minister  that  death penalty  should  not  be  the  and  other  stringent  actions  should  be  there  for  people who are involved in cases of hijacking    